    <h1>Segundo Condicional (Second Conditional)</h1>
    <p class="subtitulo">Para hablar de situaciones hipotéticas o imaginarias.</p>

    <section class="bloque">
      <h2>1. ¿Cuándo se usa?</h2>
      <p>Se usa para hablar de situaciones imaginarias, poco probables o irreales en el presente/futuro.</p>
      <div class="nota-importante">
        <b>💡 Estructura:</b> <b>If</b> + pasado simple, <b>would</b> + verbo. Ejemplo: <i>If I won the lottery, I would travel.</i>
      </div>
      <div class="tabla-vocab">
        <div class="fila-vocab"><span class="palabra-en">If I won the lottery, I would travel</span><span class="palabra-es">Si ganara la lotería, viajaría</span><button class="btn-audio" onclick="hablar('If I won the lottery, I would travel')">🔊</button></div>
        <div class="fila-vocab"><span class="palabra-en">If I were you, I would study</span><span class="palabra-es">Si yo fuera tú, estudiaría</span><button class="btn-audio" onclick="hablar('If I were you, I would study')">🔊</button></div>
        <div class="fila-vocab"><span class="palabra-en">If she had time, she would help</span><span class="palabra-es">Si ella tuviera tiempo, ayudaría</span><button class="btn-audio" onclick="hablar('If she had time, she would help')">🔊</button></div>
      </div>
      <div class="nota-importante">
        <b>💡 Dato clave:</b> Con "to be" en este condicional, se usa <b>"were"</b> para todas las personas (incluso I/he/she): <i>If I were rich...</i>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bloque">
      <h2>2. Comparación: 1er vs 2do condicional</h2>
      <ul class="lista-ejemplos">
        <li><b>If it rains, I will stay home.</b> <i>(Real y posible — 1er condicional)</i> <button class="btn-audio" onclick="hablar('If it rains, I will stay home')">🔊</button></li>
        <li><b>If I won the lottery, I would buy a house.</b> <i>(Hipotético, poco probable — 2do condicional)</i> <button class="btn-audio" onclick="hablar('If I won the lottery, I would buy a house')">🔊</button></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="bloque quiz-container">
      <h2>3. Pon a prueba lo aprendido</h2>
      <div class="pregunta" data-correcta="b">
        <p><b>1. "If I ___ (win) the lottery, I would travel":</b></p>
        <button class="opcion" onclick="revisar(this, 'a')">win</button>
        <button class="opcion" onclick="revisar(this, 'b')">won</button>
        <button class="opcion" onclick="revisar(this, 'c')">will win</button>
      </div>
      <div class="pregunta" data-correcta="c">
        <p><b>2. "If I ___ you, I would study" (Si yo fuera tú):</b></p>
        <button class="opcion" onclick="revisar(this, 'a')">am</button>
        <button class="opcion" onclick="revisar(this, 'b')">was</button>
        <button class="opcion" onclick="revisar(this, 'c')">were</button>
      </div>
      <div class="pregunta" data-correcta="a">
        <p><b>3. ¿Cuál es hipotético/poco probable?</b></p>
        <button class="opcion" onclick="revisar(this, 'a')">If I won the lottery, I would buy a house</button>
        <button class="opcion" onclick="revisar(this, 'b')">If it rains, I will stay home</button>
        <button class="opcion" onclick="revisar(this, 'c')">If you study, you will pass</button>
      </div>
      <div class="pregunta" data-correcta="b">
        <p><b>4. "If she had time, she ___ help":</b></p>
        <button class="opcion" onclick="revisar(this, 'a')">will</button>
        <button class="opcion" onclick="revisar(this, 'b')">would</button>
        <button class="opcion" onclick="revisar(this, 'c')">had</button>
      </div>
      <div id="resultado-quiz"></div>
    </section>

